com.ge.dspmicro.security.admin.api

Class SecurityAdminConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ge.dspmicro.security.admin.api.SecurityAdminConfig

  • public class SecurityAdminConfig
extends Object
    This class distributes property values to the security admin implementation classes on startup. All property values are read from the file: com.ge.dspmicro.securityadmin.cfg
